title: DDFP 639: SB LII Recap
itunes:title: DDFP 639: SB LII Recap
description:
Dave Dameshek is joined by Handsome Hank as they both recap the Philadelphia Eagles victory over the New England Patriots after watching the game in person (26:00). The guys shared their adventures from the week including Media Night, NFL Honors and how the Twin Cities treated them (55:40). Before the show ended Shek recounted his on-field celebrations with Chris Long, Malcolm Jenkins and a few of their Eagles teammates (1:13:17).
